*OpenUI *Duplex/Duplex: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 50.0 AnySetup *Duplex
*DefaultDuplex: DuplexNoTumble
*Duplex None/Off: "<</Duplex false /Tumble false>> systemdict /setpagedevice get exec"
*Duplex DuplexNoTumble/Long edge: "<</Duplex true /Tumble false>> systemdict /setpagedevice get exec"
*Duplex DuplexTumble/Short edge: "<</Duplex true /Tumble true>> systemdict /setpagedevice get exec"
*CloseUI: *Duplex

*OpenUI *Booklet/Booklet Printing: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 5.0 AnySetup *Booklet
*DefaultBooklet: Default
*Booklet Default/Printer Default: ""
*Booklet Left/On: "
<</Booklet true /BookletDetails <</Type 4 /Layout (LefttoRight)>> >> 
systemdict /setpagedevice get exec"
*End
*CloseUI: *Booklet

*OpenUI *BindMode/Saddle Stitch Setting: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 50.0 AnySetup *BindMode
